1️⃣ Download Miniconda

Copy and paste the following command exactly as it is:

wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh

2️⃣ Install Miniconda
bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh


During installation:

Press ENTER to continue

Type yes to accept the license agreement

Press ENTER to confirm the default installation path

3️⃣ Activate Conda

After installation finishes:

source ~/.bashrc

4️⃣ Verify Conda Installation
conda --version
